                              </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row row-striped">
                              <div class="col-4 text-center">
                                <div class="ml-2">
                                  <h1 class="display-5"><span class="badge badge-secondary rounded-0">9</span></h1>
                                  <h4 >AGO</h4>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                              <div class="col-8 pl-0">
                                <h4 class="text-uppercase"><strong>Nuovo film</strong></h4>
                                <ul class="list-inline">
                                  <li class="list-inline-item text-secondary font-075"><i class="fa fa-calendar-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Giovedì</li>
                                  <li class="list-inline-item text-secondary font-075"><i class="fa fa-clock-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> 2:30 PM - 4:00 PM</li>
                                  <li class="list-inline-item text-secondary font-075"><i class="fa fa-location-arrow" aria-hidden="true"></i>Biblioteca</li>
                                </ul>
                                <p>Tutti pronti che si gira il film!</p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row row-striped">
                              <div class="col-4 text-center">
                                <div class="ml-2">
                                  <h1 class="display-5"><span class="badge badge-secondary rounded-0">9</span></h1>
                                  <h4>AGO</h4>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                              <div class="col-8 pl-0">
                                <h4 class="text-uppercase"><strong>Nuovo film</strong></h4>
                                <ul class="list-inline">
                                  <li class="list-inline-item text-secondary font-075"><i class="fa fa-calendar-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Giovedì</li>
                                  <li class="list-inline-item text-secondary font-075"><i class="fa fa-clock-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> 2:30 PM - 4:00 PM</li>
                                  <li class="list-inline-item text-secondary font-075"><i class="fa fa-location-arrow" aria-hidden="true"></i>Biblioteca</li>
                                </ul>
                                <p>Tutti pronti che si gira il film!</p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>

                          <h6 class="sidebar-heading d-flex justify-content-between align-items-right px-3 mt-4 mb-1 text-muted">
                            <a class="d-flex align-items-center text-muted " href="#" style="font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase;">
